# AI notes vault

This repo is a personal idea dump for the owner. Prefer capturing thoughts into `notes/` over chatting and losing them.

When the user shares an idea, plan, or "pack this up" request:

- Write markdown under `notes/inbox/`, `notes/ideas/`, or `notes/projects/` as appropriate
- Follow `AGENTS.md` and the templates in `templates/`
- Update folder README indexes and `notes/README.md` Recent section
- Never invent details the user did not provide
